clause_text: 9. If tenanted building/s and building/s of co-operative housing society/non-tenanted building/s coexist on the plot under development, then proportionate land component as per the existing authorised BUA of existing tenanted building on the plot shall be developed as per Regulation No 33(7)(A) and remainder notional plot shall be developed as per this Regulation. 33(8) Construction of Affordable Housing in Special Development Zone (SDZ )
